3 Data Types
************

‘Numbers’
     Integers and floating-point: ‘42’, ‘-17’, ‘3.14’

‘Strings’
     Text in double quotes: ‘"hello"’, ‘"file.txt"’

‘Symbols’
     Identifiers that name variables: ‘x’, ‘buffer-insert’

‘Lists’
     Ordered collections: ‘'(1 2 3)’, ‘(list 1 2 3)’

‘Booleans’
     ‘#t’ (true), ‘#f’ (false)

‘Nil’
     Empty list / false: ‘nil’ or ‘'()’

‘Hash Maps’
     Key-value stores: ‘(hashmap "key" "value")’

‘Functions’
     Created with ‘lambda’ or ‘defun’

‘Macros’
     Created with ‘defmacro’


