4 Evaluation
************

   • *Self-evaluating*: numbers, strings, booleans, nil evaluate to
     themselves
   • *Symbols*: looked up in the current environment chain
   • *Lists*: first element is the function, remaining elements are
     evaluated as arguments
   • *Special forms*: ‘if’, ‘let’, ‘lambda’, etc.--evaluated with custom
     rules

     (+ 1 2 3)         ; function call => 6
     (if (> x 0) x 0)  ; special form
     (let ((x 10)) x)   ; special form => 10


