13 Editor API -- Cursor
***********************

 -- Function: cursor-position
     Return current cursor position as ‘(line column)’ list.
          (cursor-position)  ; => (5 10)

 -- Function: cursor-move line column
     Move cursor to LINE and COLUMN (0-indexed).

 -- Function: cursor-line
     Return current cursor line number (0-indexed).

 -- Function: cursor-column
